gmd:title.gco:CharacterString: SeaDataCloud Mediterranean Sea - V2 Temperature and Salinity Climatology

gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: The SDC_MED_CLIM_TS_V2 product contains Temperature and Salinity Climatologies for Mediterranean Sea: monthly and seasonal  fields for time periods 1955-2018, 1955-1984 and 1985-2018 and seasonal fields for 6 decades covering the time period 1955 to 2018. The climatic fields were computed from an integrated Mediterranean Sea data set that combines data extracted from SeaDataNet infrastructure (SDC_MED_DATA_TS_V2, https://doi.org/10.12770/2a2aa0c5-4054-4a62-a18b-3835b304fe64) and Coriolis Ocean Dataset for Reanalysis (CORA5.2) distributed by the Copernicus Marine Service (INSITU_GLO_TS_REP_OBSERVATIONS_013_001_b). The computation was done with the DIVAnd (Data-Interpolating Variational Analysis), version 2.4.0.

gmd:statement.gco:CharacterString:
The data used as input for this product have been extracted from the SeaDataNet Data Access Service and Copernicus Marine and Environment Monitoring Service CORA 5.2 product.
The Quality Control was performed as described in: Simona Simoncelli, Dick Schaap, Reiner Schlitzer (2020). Mediterranean Sea - Temperature and salinity Historical Data Collection SeaDataCloud V2. https://doi.org/10.12770/2a2aa0c5-4054-4a62-a18b-3835b304fe64
